	(text_box "R1 & R2 value determined by type of LED.\nI usually just stick in ≈300Ω.\nLower value, brighter LED.\nCheck the datasheet to be accurate!"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 58.42 120.65 0)
		(size 44.45 10.16)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
